# 🛡 NetSentinel – Intelligent Network Threat Detection & Auto-Mitigation Platform

NetSentinel is an advanced real-time network monitoring and threat detection system designed to identify suspicious traffic patterns and automatically mitigate critical threats.

## 🚀 Features

- Real-time packet capture using Scapy
- Traffic spike detection
- Dynamic risk scoring engine
- Severity classification (Low / Medium / High / Critical)
- Automated IP blocking (Windows Firewall)
- REST API endpoint for incidents
- Live auto-refresh dashboard
- Dark theme UI
- Modular architecture (Detection, Mitigation, API, UI)

---

## 🏗 Architecture

Network Interface  
↓  
Packet Capture Engine  
↓  
Threat Detection Engine  
↓  
Risk Scoring & Severity Classification  
↓  
Incident Logging  
↓  
Dashboard + Auto Mitigation  

---

## 🔍 Detection Capabilities

- Traffic spike detection (possible DDoS behavior)
- Suspicious IP identification
- Severity-based incident classification
- Automated blocking for Critical threats

---

## 📊 Dashboard

- Live threat monitoring
- Incident table with:
  - Source IP
  - Attack Type
  - Risk Score
  - Severity
  - Timestamp
  - Blocked Status

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- Scapy
- HTML/CSS
- REST API
- Windows Firewall (auto-block integration)

