## ⚙ Installation

1. Clone repository:

```
git clone https://github.com/hari00712/NetSentinel
cd NetSentinel
```

2. Install dependencies:

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Run as Administrator:

```
python app.py
```

4. Open:

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

